Custom GDM greeter for TAILS.

Following major parts are under development:

* dbus client for GDM service
* code implementing logon greeter
* code implementing panel

Code QA:
pylint --rcfile=.pylint.d/.pylintrc community-greeter.py
pylint --rcfile=.pylint.d/.pylintrc GdmGreeter

Test helper:

#!/bin/sh

rm tails-greeter_0.0.2_all.deb
aptitude purge tails-greeter
wget http://dev.machine/tails-greeter_0.0.2_all.deb
dpkg -i tails-greeter_0.0.2_all.deb
service gdm3 restart
